abstract: Millions of dollars in federal contracts intended for small businesses reportedly were awarded to companies that had not qualified or had won the contracts fraudulently.
snippet: Millions of dollars in federal contracts intended for small businesses reportedly were awarded to companies that had not qualified or had won the contracts fraudulently.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON  Two government reports have uncovered millions of dollars in federal contracts that were supposed to go to small businesses but instead were awarded to companies that had not qualified or had obtained the contracts fraudulently.

abstract: In Las Vegas, the United States men’s basketball team began its final workouts before heading over to China.
snippet: In Las Vegas, the United States men’s basketball team began its final workouts before heading over to China.
lead_paragraph: LAS VEGAS – The setting for the final leg of the rebranding of USA Basketball fittingly began in the humblest of places. At Valley High School, in a nondescript building about two miles of the Strip, Team USA began its final workouts before heading over to China to begin its project of reclaiming what the players and coaches perceive as the country’s rightful spot atop the world basketball hierarchy.
